     <S id="S9">
          <FORM>7 Ka ni-koun tyn tyni-æn, 'Ou-kou-koua madioep-pa [ym-houan] tou æizug-han ki Siloe (ka pattæ'i-toun noun-nun ki sou, ni-padingi-en.) Ka ni-'ouk-oun tyn madi oep[tyni-æn,] ka ieroua-ato ka kmyt'-ato.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S11">
          <FORM>8 Annata kahalahalau-an, ne-ni-appa ka ni-kmytta tyni-n ka-lahei ka mavoutta-appa, ta ni-k'ma, Assi kauwa teni ta ni-mier-raoung kanna tmoumymmia ki tæ'-esh ki harum?</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S13">
          <FORM>9 Ni-k''ma tararouma, Teni k'anna: rarouma-appa, Mahau-wei tyni-æn. Ni-k'ma ta teni, Ti jau k'atta.</FORM>
     </S>
     <S id="S15">
          <FORM>10 Annatanik'ma ta neni ty-ni, Ni-pa-r'kyllat-ten ke wmama ki mang ki matta ?</FORM>
